race.comment: WOODSIDE VIXEN (8) was sent out big odds but was a fast winner (26.12) last time in a Grade 5 at Warragul. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Ideally placed to take this out. JOEY (4) has missed the frame the last couple but just a few runs back pushed the clock when winning over 510m at this track, taking a T3 RSTW in a speedy 28.79. Has the ability and can find winning form again. AUDACIOUS PADDY (5) boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 1.1 lengths (29.06) behind Paw Harry at this track. The form out of his last race has been franked. Can measure up. JAIRON BALE (1) is worth including.
